# add-zero-left

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `arithmetic_simplification_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (add (const-int 0) ?x)
rhs: ?x
